                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830723-45-off205 t17830723-45-cd206"></join> last, eighty-four pounds weight of lead, value 10 s. belonging to 
                     
                        <persName id="t17830723-45-victim516" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Barker
                        <interp inst="t17830723-45-victim516" type="surname" value="Barker"></interp>
